Texts.Chs: 把的^green;氢气^reset;带给紫色的蚁族人(位于^orange;科学前哨站^reset;)
Texts.Eng: Bring the ^green;Hydrogen^reset; to the purple Thelusian at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;

Texts.Chs: 非常感谢，现在我终于可以完成这个能量电池了，这些是给你的奖励。
Texts.Eng: Great. Thanks so very much. Now I can complete this power cell! Take this as payment for your deeds.

Texts.Chs: 我们从不缺^orange;水^reset;。如果你升级了你的^orange;物质枪^reset;，能拾取水...^green;萃取一些水^reset;并给我5份^orange;氢气^reset;，你乐意吗？
Texts.Eng: ^orange;Water^reset; is never in short supply. If you have upgraded your ^orange;Matter Manipulator^reset; to pick up liquids...^green;extract some^reset; and bring me 5 ^orange;Hydrogen^reset; if you don't mind?
